OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a bus driver died
OL,8,Ffollowing an assault on Battersea
OL,9,FBridge in London.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police said the
OL,12,Fdriver was assaulted following a
OL,13,Fconfrontation on the pavement while
OL,14,Fhis bus was parked at a stop shortly
OL,15,Fbefore 12.30am on Monday.
OL,17,FThat man, who has been named by police
OL,18,Fas Sergei Krajev, 64, was rushed to
OL,19,Fhospital by London's Air Ambulance
OL,20,Fwhere he died the next day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
