CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779361379
OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,FGary Jones, 32, of no fixed address,
OL,7,Fwas remanded into custody on Tuesday
OL,8,Fafter appearing at Wimbledon
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court charged with
OL,10,Fcausing grievous bodily harm, police
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FJones will next appear at Kingston
OL,14,FCrown Court on June 15.
OL,16,FIn a tribute, Mr Krajev's family said:
OL,17,F"We feel fortunate to have had such a
OL,18,Fwonderful husband, father, and
OL,19,Fgrandfather in our lives.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779361379
OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,F"He was a thoughtful, tactful, and
OL,7,Fconscientious person who cared about
OL,8,Fthose around him.
OL,10,F"In his role as a bus driver, he was
OL,11,Fpunctual, reliable and willing to help.
OL,13,F"He valued good relationships with his
OL,14,Fcolleagues and approached his duties
OL,15,Fwith care and dedication.
OL,17,F"We are grateful to the police
OL,18,Fofficers, healthcare workers and
OL,19,Femergency services involved for their
OL,20,Fcare, professionalism and compassion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779361379
OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are also with other
OL,7,Fpublic-facing transport workers who
OL,8,Fmay be distressed or alarmed by this
OL,9,Fnews."
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Sarah Lee, who is
OL,12,Fleading the investigation, said: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts are with Sergei's family,
OL,14,Ffriends and colleagues after this
OL,15,Ftragic incident.
OL,17,F"We recognise the concern this will
OL,18,Fcause within the local community and
OL,19,Famong those who work across our public
OL,20,Ftransport network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]tD@bOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779361379
OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,F"We want to reassure those impacted
OL,7,Fthat our officers are working closely
OL,8,Fwith Transport for London as part of
OL,9,Four investigation."
OL,11,FSiwan Hayward, director of security,
OL,12,Fpolicing and enforcement at Transport
OL,13,Ffor London, said they are "devastated"
OL,14,Fby the death of their colleague Mr
OL,15,FKrajev and are supporting the police
OL,16,Fwith the investigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]uD@[OUuD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
