OL,3,CMurder investigation over death of bus
OL,4,Cdriver after Battersea Bridge attack
OL,6,FShe said: "We take all forms of
OL,7,Fviolence extremely seriously and
OL,8,Fremain committed to protecting our
OL,9,Fstaff and customers across the
OL,10,Fnetwork, taking the strongest possible
OL,11,Faction against anyone committing
OL,12,Fviolence or abuse.
OL,14,F"We will not stand for any violence or
OL,15,Faggression and will continue to do
OL,16,Feverything possible to protect
OL,17,Feveryone's right to go to work and
OL,18,Ftravel without fear or intimidation."
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
